Hey everyone! I'm thrilled to share something close to my heart with all of you. 🌟 Introducing the MrsMD Weight Loss Support Group – a vibrant, new community on Facebook designed to empower, inspire, and support each other on our weight loss journeys. 

I've been where you are, and I know how crucial support is in achieving our wellness goals. That's why I wanted to create a space where we can share tips, celebrate progress, and uplift each other every step of the way. 

🏋️‍♀️ Whether you're just starting out, looking to maintain your achievements, or searching for new methods to re-energize your routine, this group is here for YOU.

- Regular insights and tips from my own weight loss journey.

I feel like a new person and am truly thankful for the years that I added back onto my life when I lost 80lbs.

My Aunt was more like a sister to me. She was only five years older than me. It’s been 12 years but the pain of losing her doesn’t go away. This time of year is sad for our family but also happy because we were blessed with her beautiful, loving, smart, kind and sweet daughter. 
We must require the state of GA to take immediate action. I will be joining @parkcannon58 and @lydiaglaizedistrict67 on Jan 23rd to ensure that Black mothers are Heard, BELIEVED and Treated. #blackmaternalmortality #blackwomenmatter #georgia #RIPAuntDeeDee
